Society.Lands:
Crystal dragons were known to live on the [[High Ice]], north of [[Anauroch]]. However, so too did their white dragon rivals, and they regularly clashed when they came across one another. The crystal dragons had also wiped out frost giants that had tried to settle in the area.{{ Cite book/Elminster's Ecologies/Anauroch|20}}

The northern [[Thunder Peaks]], east of [[Cormyr]] were cool enough to support but one gem dragon, who was a crystal dragon in the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].

In the [[Unapproachable East]], crystal dragons could be found in the hills and mountains of [[Rashemen]].<ref>

document_data.Known Crystal Dragons:
* [[Hrodel]], a thane of the gem dragon deity [[Sardior]], the Ruby Dragon.{{Cite web/The Legend of Sardior}}
* [[Saryndalaghlothtor]], "Lady Gemcloak", who lived with the [[House of the Axe]] [[dwarves]] of the [[Crags]] and [[Mirabar]].<ref><ref>{{Cite web/Wyrms of the North/Saryndalaghlothtor, "Lady Gemcloak"}}{{Cite web enhancement/Roll Call of Dragons}}
* [[Yiarni]], the kindly adult crystal dragon of the Thunder Peaks.<ref>
* [[Klaruuotur]], ancient guardian of the family of the djinni lord [[Calim]].<ref>
* [[Krustalonos]], companion of the mage [[Tulrun|Tulrun of the Tent]].<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/125/Wayward Wizards: Tulrun of the Tent|24}}
